casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

92-282. St. Elizabeth Hosp. Med. Ctr. v. Moliterno.

Mahoning County, No. 89 C.A. 185. This cause, here on appeal from the Court of Appeals for Mahoning County, was considered in the manner prescribed by law. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss this appeal at appellee’s costs,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective October 20, 1992.
